=========================================
DESIGN PATTERNS FOR C++ INTERVIEWS
Most Asked → Least Asked
=========================================

TIER 1 (MUST DO) ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
-----------------------------------------

1. Singleton Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Why:
- Most frequently asked pattern
- Follow-up questions on thread safety

Must Know:
- Lazy Initialization
- Eager Initialization
- Thread-Safe Singleton (Meyers Singleton)
- Deleted Copy Constructor
- Deleted Assignment Operator

Interview Questions:
- Implement Singleton
- Make Singleton thread-safe
- Problems with Singleton

-----------------------------------------

2. Factory Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Why:
- Very common in LLD interviews

Must Know:
- Object creation abstraction
- Runtime object creation

Interview Questions:
- What problem does Factory solve?
- Factory vs Simple Object Creation?
- Real-world examples?

-----------------------------------------

3. Strategy Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Why:
- Frequently asked with SOLID (OCP)

Must Know:
- Runtime behavior change
- Composition over inheritance

Interview Questions:
- Explain with payment example
- Benefits over if-else chains

-----------------------------------------

4. Observer Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Why:
- Common LLD question

Examples:
- YouTube subscribers
- Stock price updates
- Notification systems

Interview Questions:
- Publisher vs Subscriber
- How notification mechanism works

-----------------------------------------

5. Adapter Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Why:
- Very common practical example

Examples:
- Legacy code integration
- Different API interfaces

Interview Questions:
- Adapter vs Wrapper?
- Real-world use cases?

=========================================

TIER 2 (FREQUENTLY ASKED) ⭐⭐⭐⭐
-----------------------------------------

6. Decorator Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Examples:
- Coffee customization
- Logging
- Feature additions

Interview Questions:
- Decorator vs Inheritance?

-----------------------------------------

7. Abstract Factory
-----------------------------------------
Examples:
- Cross-platform UI
- Windows/Linux/Mac widgets

Interview Questions:
- Factory vs Abstract Factory?

-----------------------------------------

8. Builder Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Examples:
- Complex object creation
- SQL Query Builder

Interview Questions:
- Builder vs Factory?

-----------------------------------------

9. Command Pattern
-----------------------------------------
Examples:
- Undo/Redo
- Remote Control

Interview Questions:
- How undo operation works?

=========================================

TIER 3 (GOOD TO KNOW) ⭐⭐⭐
-----------------------------------------

10. Template Method

11. State Pattern

12. Chain of Responsibility

13. Facade Pattern

14. Proxy Pattern

15. Flyweight Pattern

