=========================================
MOST ASKED INTERVIEW QUESTIONS
=========================================

1. Implement Singleton in C++
2. How to make Singleton thread-safe?
3. Factory vs Abstract Factory?
4. Strategy vs State Pattern?
5. Why prefer Strategy over if-else?
6. Observer Pattern real-world example?
7. Decorator vs Inheritance?
8. Builder vs Factory?
9. Adapter Pattern example?
10. Which design patterns have you used in projects?

=========================================
IF SHORT ON TIME
=========================================

Prepare thoroughly:

1. Singleton
2. Factory
3. Strategy
4. Observer
5. Adapter

Then move to:

6. Decorator
7. Abstract Factory
8. Builder

For most 10+ year C++ interviews, these 8 patterns are sufficient.
